.TH "update_statusp" 9 "update_statusp" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
update_statusp \- Update userspace status flag
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" update_statusp
.BI "(struct hfi1_pportdata *ppd "  ","
.BI "u32 state "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ppd" 12
Port data structure
.IP "state" 12
port state information
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Actual port status is determined by the host_link_state value
in the ppd.

host_link_state MUST be updated before updating the user space
statusp.
